      <hedline>
        <hl1>A Reminder to Wash</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Jeffrey H Tigay letter suggests signs be posted in public toilets to remind everyone to wash their hands (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>A Sept. 21 letter pointing out the dangers to oneself and others of failing to wash after using the lavatory prompts this suggestion: Perhaps state and local health departments should require that signs be posted in all public restrooms advising all users, not just employees, to wash and noting those dangers -- especially those to oneself.</p>
        <p>JEFFREY H. TIGAY  Wynnewood, Pa., Sept. 21, 2000</p>
      </block>
